an say that I discovered a magnificent film with incredible emotions, saying that it deserved the Oscar in relation to "La La Land" there, I'm sure, but I also loved, " You will not kill "and" Fences "two who would have largely earned the Oscar for best film. This is a wonderful film that I advise to see for all the positives detailed in my review
