This movie had zero plot. Zero. Usually when someone "explores" their sexuality, you're exploring between 2 or more different decisions. This kid was gay and he knew it the whole entire time. The acting was poor. The best actor was Juan the drug dealer and that's not saying much, and then they killed him off and his girlfriend disappears out of nowhere.

